      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "color":{"mode":"thresholds"}, "custom":{"fillOpacity":80,"lineWidth":1}, "thresholds":{"mode":"absolute","steps":[{"color":"red","value":null},{"color":"yellow","value":50},{"color":"green","value":80}]}, "unit":"percent", "min":0, "max":100 }, "overrides":[] },
